<div id="content"><a name="content"></a>
 <h2>Features</h2>
  <h3>Current</h3>

<ul>
  <li>An editor for captioning post production video</li>
  <li>A preview area with several layout options
  <li>A variety of export options
      <ul>
        <li>Timed Text (DFXP)</li>
        <li>DVD STL</li>
        <li>MicroDVD</li>
        <li>QT text</li>
        <li>SAMI</li>
        <li>SubRip</li>
        <li>SubViewer</li>
      </ul>
  </li>
  <li>A project package export that includes an accessible player</li>
  <li>Support for several import caption formats</li>
</ul>

<h3>Coming Soon</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Audio description creation and editing</li>
  <li>Import voice-recognition output for "cleaning up"</li>
  <li>Transcription notes</li>
  <li>WSYWIG editor for captions</li>
  <li>ATAG compliance</li>
</ul>

<h3>Future</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Export for iTunes caption format (SCC)</li>
  <li>Admin tools</li>
  <li>Real time captioning</li>
  <li>Collaborative captioning</li>
  <li>Captioned video repository</li>
  <li>Mobile support</li>
  <li>Multiple video tracks</li>
</ul>
